                            <comment id="14465776" author="wabrit" created="Tue, 16 Dec 2008 05:29:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Apologies for inadvertently creating emoticons. Hopefully this will be more readable&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;************************************************************************************************&lt;br/&gt;
def x=&quot;&amp;lt;Foo xmlns=&apos;urn:a&apos; xmlns:f=&apos;urn:a&apos;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;f:Bar xmlns=&apos;urn:b&apos;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;haha/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/f:Bar&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/Foo&amp;gt;&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
def y = new XmlParser(false, true).parseText( x )&lt;br/&gt;
def writer = new StringWriter()&lt;br/&gt;
def xnp = new XmlNodePrinter(new PrintWriter(writer))&lt;br/&gt;
xnp.namespaceAware = true&lt;br/&gt;
xnp.print( y )&lt;br/&gt;
print writer.toString()&lt;br/&gt;
************************************************************************************************&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Output is  - note missing declaration for namespace prefix &quot;f:&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

